s</i> 13(6) 1215–1229. DOI:<a href=&quot;https://doi.org/10.1007/s13300-022-01269-1&quot;>10.1007/s13300-022-01269-1</a>  PUBMED:<a href=&quot;https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35543870/&quot;>https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35543870</a></p></li></ol></body></html>",
